blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Cufoo and Maroshao Cubone and Mienfoo fusion and Marowak and Mienshao fusion Both are Ground/Fighting Type Both have the ability...
caption:
Cufoo and Maroshao

Cubone and Mienfoo fusion and Marowak and Mienshao fusion

Both are Ground/Fighting Type

Both have the ability Reckless

Cufoo - The Bone Bashing Pokemon

Maroshao - The Bone Attacking Pokemon

Cufoo is a natural fighter and fights to protect its family.  As long as it can find a bone, it can fight.  The red puffs on its arms are thick muscle.

Maroshao’s bone structure on its arms are made from soft bone.  It can attack using its cheek bones and bone whips on its arms.  It’s actually rather quick on its feet.

Request for @cr-tist. I hope you like it! Sorry it took so long!
